&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;LONDON NORTH WEST UNIVERSITY HEALTHCARE TRUST&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NORTHWICK PARK HOSPITAL – HARROW COMMUNITY SERVICES&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;PAEDIATRIC THERAPY SERVICES&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;BAND 6: SPECIALIST PAEDIATRIC PHYSIOTHERAPIST &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;1.0 WTE –37.5 Hours&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking an enthusiastic Physiotherapist to join our Paediatric rotational scheme in Harrow. This scheme offers the opportunity to gain a broad experience in Paediatrics through yearly rotations in the following areas of services:-&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Acute/Orthopaedics&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Pre-school Special Needs &amp; Special Schools&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Schools Services (mainstream and special schools)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Based within a multidisciplinary team, we can offer you well established support/supervision systems, access to in-house/external training programmes and regular appraisal and individual development plans.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Northwick Park Hospital has one of the largest Paediatric Therapy Teams in North West London. You would work along side colleagues in Occupational Therapy and Speech &amp; Language Therapy, providing both acute and community services in the London Borough of Harrow. We are a well established, dynamic team based in a purpose-built children’s centre where there is collaborative working practices with colleagues in Health, Education and Social Services.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Northwick Park Hospital is excellently situated just 20 minutes from central London on the Metropolitan line . En-suite accommodation is available on site.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NameSamantha BishoppJob titleLead of Paediatric PhysiotherapyEmail addresssamantha.bishopp@nhs.netTelephone number020 8869 2519Additional contact information&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For informal discussions or visit please call please call Samantha Bishopp, Lead of Paediatric Physiotherapy on 0208 869 2519 - Northwick Park Hospital or &lt;br /&gt;e-mail: samantha.bishopp@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
